OL,3,C'They've taken my life too' - murdered
OL,4,Cboy's mum sees teen killers sentenced
OL,6,FMr Justice Saini imposed a life
OL,7,Fsentence at Bristol Crown Court on
OL,8,FFriday 3 May and ordered that
OL,9,FCunningham should serve a minimum term
OL,10,Fof 16 years custody before he can be
OL,11,Fconsidered for parole.
OL,13,FHayley Ryall remembered her son,
OL,14,FMikey, who lost his life on 10 June
OL,15,Flast year, as a "fun and fearless"
OL,16,Fchild.
OL,18,F"Every day he told me he loved me, he
OL,19,Fdidn't care if there were 10 friends
OL,20,Faround him", she said.
