OL,3,C'They've taken my life too' - murdered
OL,4,Cboy's mum sees teen killers sentenced
OL,6,F"The last thing I said to him was:
OL,7,F'You look really handsome' and he was
OL,8,Flike: 'Thanks mum" and got embarrassed
OL,9,Fabout it."
OL,11,FThe following night, on 10 June, while
OL,12,FHayley was away on a work trip,
OL,14,F"I can remember saying: 'You're lying,
OL,15,Fyou're lying, why are you lying?'",
OL,16,Fshe said, as she remembered the moment
OL,17,Fthat changed her life forever.
