OL,3,C'They've taken my life too' - murdered
OL,4,Cboy's mum sees teen killers sentenced
OL,6,FHayley sat through the entire five-and-
OL,7,Fa-half week trial of the three
OL,8,Fteenagers, who had never met her son,
OL,9,Fas they were found responsible for his
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,F"They've taken Mikey's life, all his
OL,13,Fdreams, all his hopes", Hayley said.
OL,15,F"He probably would've been running his
OL,16,Fown business, because that's how he
OL,17,Fwas. They've taken that away from him.
OL,19,F"He won't have kids. I won't have
OL,20,Fgrandkids. You can't just choose to
OL,21,Ftake someone's dreams away.
